name: simulakrum
description:
Humans are complex and unique creatures, they create reality based on their own ideas. therefore, every day we are treated to an artificial reality created by the media.
The media no longer reflects reality, even becomes reality itself.
Simulacrum (from Latin simulacrum, meaning "likeness, resemblance"). Simulacrum means the world with the expropriation of truth by fictitious, rhetorical, and false truths; pseudo reality.
